org.hbase.async.auth

Class KerberosClientAuthProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hbase.async.auth.ClientAuthProvider
      • org.hbase.async.auth.KerberosClientAuthProvider

  • public class KerberosClientAuthProvider
extends ClientAuthProvider
    Handles Kerberos based authentication using the Java Authentication and Authorization Service (JAAS). The class requires a few settings including: asynchbase.security.auth.kerberos.regionserver.principal - a principal name or template to use for authentication. The value can have the token "_HOST" which will be replaced with the cannonical name of the localhost.
    Since:
    1.7
